structure.unit: CLASSIFICATION AND DESIGNATION OF OFFENSES -- AUTHORIZED DISPOSITION

law.catch_line: Chapters 532, 533 and 534 to apply to crimes outside provisions of the Penal Code.
law.text: KRS Chapters 532, 533 and 534 apply to all classes of crimes committed outside the provisions of the Penal Code.
law.history: Created 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 183, sec. 6, effective June 19, 1976.
